It's a small fy_map in the dev textures. Also it's my first map I released. So I hope you like it. The sides of T's and CT's are simmilar to each other so that everyone has same conditions. the weapons are spawning on the ground and there's only 1 AWP behind a breakable door on the top floor. - 24 spawns - spawning weapons - 1 AWP - dev_textures
v1.1: - added nav-file created by chizbone - corrected the Spawns CREDITS: - offroad - chizbone (nav-file)
